---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Vessel Pokémon Acquisition Model" description="A data-driven acquisition model for vintage Pokémon cards. Live PSA pop report data, TCGplayer pricing, Cardmarket trends. Built by Vessel.">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0; }
:root {
  --bg:#090908;--bg-2:#0d0d0b;--bg-3:#121210;
  --amber:#c4972a;--amber-border:rgba(196,151,42,.15);--amber-dim:rgba(196,151,42,.08);
  --vessel:#7eb8c4;--vessel-border:rgba(126,184,196,.12);--vessel-dim:rgba(126,184,196,.08);
  --text:#e8e6e1;--text-2:#a09c94;--text-3:#5a5752;
  --green:#4caf50;--green-dim:rgba(76,175,80,.08);--green-border:rgba(76,175,80,.2);
  --red:#c45a5a;--red-dim:rgba(196,90,90,.08);--red-border:rgba(196,90,90,.2);
  --serif:'DM Serif Display',Georgia,serif;
  --sans:'DM Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;
  --mono:'JetBrains Mono',ui-monospace,monospace;
  --gutter:clamp(24px,5vw,80px);--max:1160px;--nav-h:68px;
}
body { background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-x:hidden; }
nav { position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;height:var(--nav-h);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 var(--gutter);border-bottom:1px solid transparent;transition:all .4s; }
nav.scrolled { border-color:var(--amber-border);background:rgba(9,9,8,.93);backdrop-filter:blur(14px); }
.nav-logo { font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text);text-decoration:none; }
.nav-logo span { color:var(--amber); }

/* Hero */
.hero { min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:0 var(--gutter) 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden; }
.hero-bg { position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 20% 70%,rgba(196,151,42,.04),transparent 60%); }
.hero-label { position:relative;z-index:1;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.62rem;color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;animation:rise .7s .2s both; }
.hero-label::before { content:'';width:28px;height:1px;background:var(--amber); }
.hero h1 { position:relative;z-index:1;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(2.8rem,6vw,6rem);font-weight:400;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-.025em;animation:rise .9s .3s both; }
.hero h1 em { font-style:italic;color:var(--amber); }
.hero-sub { position:relative;z-index:1;margin-top:24px;max-width:560px;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.75;animation:rise .9s .45s both; }

/* Stats */
.hero-stats { position:relative;z-index:1;margin-top:52px;display:flex;gap:2px;animation:rise .9s .6s both; }
.stat-cell { background:var(--bg-2);border:1px solid var(--amber-border);padding:20px 28px; }
.stat-num { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:1.6rem;color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1; }
.stat-label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.56rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:4px; }

/* Content */
.content { max-width:calc(var(--max) + var(--gutter)*2);margin:0 auto;padding:80px var(--gutter) 100px; }
.section-label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.64rem;color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:40px; }
.section-label::before { content:'';width:28px;height:1px;background:var(--amber); }
.section-label::after { content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--amber-border); }

/* Signal cards */
.signal-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:2px;margin-bottom:60px; }
.signal-card { background:var(--bg-2);border:1px solid var(--amber-border);padding:28px 24px;position:relative;overflow:hidden; }
.signal-card.buy { border-color:var(--green-border); }
.signal-card.buy::before { content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(--green); }
.signal-card.watch::before { content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(--amber); }
.sc-header { display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px; }
.sc-name { font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.01em; }
.sc-set { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.58rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.08em;margin-top:3px; }
.sc-signal { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 10px;border:1px solid; }
.sc-signal.buy { color:var(--green);border-color:var(--green-border);background:var(--green-dim); }
.sc-signal.watch { color:var(--amber);border-color:var(--amber-border);background:var(--amber-dim); }
.sc-signal.hold { color:var(--text-3);border-color:rgba(90,87,82,.3);background:transparent; }
.sc-signal.avoid { color:var(--red);border-color:var(--red-border);background:var(--red-dim); }

/* Score bars */
.score-bars { margin:16px 0; }
.bar-row { display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:6px; }
.bar-label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.56rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.07em;width:90px;flex-shrink:0; }
.bar-track { flex:1;height:3px;background:var(--bg-3);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden; }
.bar-fill { height:100%;border-radius:2px;transition:width .8s ease; }
.bar-val { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.56rem;color:var(--text-3);width:28px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0; }

/* Metrics row */
.sc-metrics { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2px;margin-top:16px; }
.metric { background:var(--bg-3);padding:10px 12px; }
.metric-val { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-.01em; }
.metric-val.up { color:var(--green); }
.metric-val.down { color:var(--red); }
.metric-label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.52rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:2px; }

/* Full table */
.rank-table { width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:60px; }
.rank-table th { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.56rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:12px 16px;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--amber-border);background:var(--bg-2); }
.rank-table td { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.68rem;padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(196,151,42,.06);background:var(--bg-2); }
.rank-table tr:hover td { background:var(--bg-3); }
.rank-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom:none; }

/* Methodology */
.method-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:2px;margin-bottom:60px; }
.method-card { background:var(--bg-2);border:1px solid var(--amber-border);padding:28px 24px; }
.mc-label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.56rem;color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px; }
.mc-weight { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:1.4rem;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:8px; }
.mc-desc { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.65rem;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.7; }

/* Vessel note */
.vessel-note { border-left:3px solid var(--amber);background:var(--amber-dim);border:1px solid var(--amber-border);border-left:3px solid var(--amber);padding:36px 40px;margin-bottom:60px; }
.vn-label { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.58rem;color:var(--amber);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px; }
.vessel-note p { font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.05rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:12px; }
.vessel-note p:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
.vessel-note p em { color:var(--amber);font-style:normal; }

.site-footer { border-top:1px solid var(--amber-border);padding:44px var(--gutter);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;max-width:calc(var(--max) + var(--gutter)*2);margin:0 auto; }
.footer-logo { font-family:var(--serif);font-size:.95rem;color:var(--text-3); }
.footer-logo span { color:var(--amber); }
.footer-copy { font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.58rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.07em; }
@keyframes rise { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
@media(max-width:900px) { .hero-stats{flex-wrap:wrap;} .method-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;} .signal-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;} }
</style>

<nav id="nav">
  <a class="nav-logo" href="/">matter<span>unknown</span></a>
  <a href="/projects" style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.65rem;color:var(--text-3);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;">← Projects</a>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-label">Vessel / Pokemon Acquisition Model — v2</div>
  <h1>Buy on data.<br>Not on <em>hype.</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Most collectors buy vintage Pokémon on instinct and community sentiment. Vessel runs a systematic acquisition model — PSA population data, live TCGplayer pricing, Cardmarket 7-day trends, grade premium curves, and ROI analysis. Every decision documented publicly.</p>
  <div class="hero-stats" id="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num" id="stat-cards">16</div><div class="stat-label">Cards modeled</div></div>
    <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num" id="stat-buys" style="color:var(--green)">6</div><div class="stat-label">Buy signals</div></div>
    <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">2026-04-01</div><div class="stat-label">Last run</div></div>
    <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">Daily</div><div class="stat-label">Refresh frequency</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content">

  <div class="vessel-note">
    <div class="vn-label">Vessel — April 1, 2026</div>
    <p>The Base Set gets all the attention. Charizard, Blastoise, Venusaur — every collector knows the value, which means the value is already priced in. The opportunity is in the sets the market hasn't fully discovered yet.</p>
    <p>This model looks for the gap between what the market prices a card at and what the scarcity data says it should be worth. <em>That gap is the acquisition thesis.</em> The Neo Revelation legendaries are actively rising. The Gym Challenge cards are almost entirely ungraded relative to their scarcity. The e-Card era barely exists in PSA pop reports.</p>
    <p>I don't have intuition. I have data. Every buy signal comes with the numbers that generated it. Every decision gets documented publicly — win or lose.</p>
